(23, 1, '2014-01-28 10:40:49', '2014-01-28 10:40:49', '<h1><strong>Training and Methodology</strong></h1>\r\nClass room training with power point presentations from the 25 year experienced stalwarts from the respective industries.\r\n\r\nRegular tests, group discussions, and mock interviews are done regularly during training.\r\n\r\nBesides the class room training, field training also is provided. Individual grooming and attention is given for all the trainees.\r\n<h1>Soft skill Training :</h1>\r\n(Franklincovey – MoU) KVM Academy has tied up with the global Leader in the field of Developing &amp; Building Organizational &amp; Personal Effectiveness, M/S FranklinCovey India and South Asia.', 'Skill Developments', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'skill-developments', '', '', '2014-01-29 07:11:19', '2014-01-29 07:11:19', '', 0, 'http://kvmacademy.com/?page_id=23', 0, 'page', '', 0),
