(33, 1, '2014-01-28 10:50:25', '2014-01-28 10:50:25', '<h1><strong>Enrollment Process</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Level 1: </strong>Interested students contact us\r\n\r\n<strong>Level 2: </strong> Appointment will be scheduled and students need to walk-in our centre for a discussion with our Students counsellor.\r\n\r\n<strong>Level 3: </strong>After Selection process Students need to fill in an application form at the centre with a copy of your  2 passport size photos + a copy of your latest school / college mark sheet.\r\n\r\n<strong>Level 4:</strong> Students officially enroll into KVM Academy after payment of fees.', 'Enrollment Process', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'enrollment-process', '', '', '2014-01-29 07:15:04', '2014-01-29 07:15:04', '', 0, 'http://kvmacademy.com/?page_id=33', 0, 'page', '', 0),
