(219, 1, '2014-02-11 12:20:40', '2014-02-11 12:20:40', '<h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>\n<p>We have listed some often asked questions in this section. We hope the information here will answer your doubts.</p>\n[su_accordion]\n  [su_spoiler title="Q : What is KVM Academy?"] A: [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Q: Who Can Apply for the Course? What are the eligibility criteria?"] A: For the Healthcare and Wellness course, students who have passed their Under-graduates and above can apply. For the Hospitality and retail courses students who have passed their Std XII and above can apply. [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Q: I''ve just completed Std VIII. Can I apply?"] A: No, you should have passed or appeared for Std XII exam. [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Q: I dropped out when I was in Std XII. Will my application be eligible?"] A: Your application will be eligible for the Hospitality and Retail course. [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Q: I do not live in chennai but I am interested in applying for the course. Will you help me with a hostel facility?"] A: We do not provide hostel facilities on our own but we would be more than willing to assist you to find something suitable. [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Q: I''ve Misplaced my certificates. Can I still apply?"] A: Sorry, you cannot apply [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Q: Is there an age criterion?"] A: Yes, you have to be between 18 to 27 years. [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Q: What is the language in which the course is conducted?"] A: All our courses are conducted in English and Regional Languages [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Q: What are the courses available?"] A: Health Care and Wellness : 15 days short term course in "Pharmaceutical Selling" enabling the trainees to become Medical Sales Representatives successfully.\nHospitality and Tourism : 5 days short term course in "Hotel Management" enabling the trainees to become Stewards, Waiters successfully.\nBanking and Financial Services, Retail and Insurance courses will be handled in due course of time. [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Q: Are the classes on Saturdays?"] A: Yes. [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Q: How many students do you take per Batch?"] A: Not more than 30 students to ensure teachers are able to give attention to all students. [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Q: What are the class timings?"] A: Classes take place in 2 batches.\nMorning : 9.30am to 1.00 pm\nEvening : 2.00pm to 6.00pm [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Q: I am a part-time working professional; can there be change in timings for me to pursue the course?"] A : You can choose either the morning batch or the evening batch according your timings [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Do you provide any conveyance / transport facilitates?"] A : No [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Q: Is there a dress-code for your institute?"]  A: Yes. It is formal wear only. [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Q: Can a student take 2 courses at a time?"] A: No. Because the courses are very intensive including a lot of project work and exercises that you have to prepare for. And we can only get you one job, not two at a time.t [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Q: At the end of the course do I get certificate?  Or mark sheet? What will my qualification be?"] A : We  provide certificates for those who complete the training successfully. At the end of the course you are guaranteed a job with a reputed company. We don''t give out mark sheets because we don''t mark our students. [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Q: What placement surety do you give?"] A: We fully assure placements to all trainees. [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Q: What is the average starting salary a student receives after placement from your institute?"] Spoiler content [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Spoiler title"] Spoiler content [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Spoiler title"] Spoiler content [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Spoiler title"] Spoiler content [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Spoiler title"] Spoiler content [/su_spoiler]\n  [su_spoiler title="Spoiler title"] Spoiler content [/su_spoiler]\n[/su_accordion]', 'FAQ', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '29-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-02-11 12:20:40', '2014-02-11 12:20:40', '', 29, 'http://kvmacademy.com/29-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
