learance at all levels. He has played a major part in the overall management of new strategies and initiatives taken up by KVM Group. He was earlier involved in designing and creating detailed architectural drawings for projects like schools, residences, hotels, hospitals and coordination with site. He is also experienced in the promotional and brand building activities for a famous township at Chennai.', 'Management Team', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '128-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-02-13 06:51:30', '2014-02-13 06:51:30', '', 128, 'http://kvmacademy.com/128-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
