(305, 1, '2014-02-13 08:16:59', '2014-02-13 08:16:59', '<div class="kvm-post-inner">\r\n<h1 class="kvm-postheader"><strong>Academic Council</strong></h1>\r\n<div class="kvm-postcontent">\r\n<div class="kvm-article">\r\n\r\nAn academic council comprising of distinguished educationalists, professors and consultants, has been created to advise and oversee the standard of programs offered by the Academy. The members are:\r\n<div class="fleft p10 Mb10 w25"><center>Prof. Mathew Manimala, Head OB, IIM Bangalore<a href="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Mathew_Manimala.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-310 aligncenter" alt="Mathew_Manimala" src="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Mathew_Manimala.jpg" width="200" height="200" /></a></center></div>\r\n<div class="fleft p10 Mb10 w25"><center>Prof. V. B. Kaujalgi, Former IT Professor, Bangalore<a href="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Kaujalgi.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-309 aligncenter" alt="Kaujalgi" src="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Kaujalgi.jpg" width="200" height="200" /></a></center></div>\r\n<div class="fleft p10 Mb10 w25"><center>Mr. Vasanth M Cavale, Management Consultant (IIM Ahmedabad)<a href="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Vasant_Cavale.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-314 aligncenter" alt="Vasant_Cavale" src="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Vasant_Cavale.jpg" width="200" height="200" /></a></center></div>\r\n<div class="fleft p10 Mb10 w25"><center>Mr. Selvam George, CEO, 5Eserpraises (XLRI Jamshedpur)<a href="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Selvam_George.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-313 aligncenter" alt="Selvam_George" src="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Selvam_George.jpg" width="200" height="200" /></a></center></div>\r\n<div class="fleft p10 Mb10 w25"><center>Dr. N. Ravichandran, CEO, Lucas TVS, Chennai<a href="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Ravichandran.jpg"><