(332, 1, '2014-02-13 10:36:21', '2014-02-13 10:36:21', '<h1><strong>Our Management Team</strong></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<strong> <a href="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Madhan.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-263 alignleft" alt="Madhan" src="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Madhan.jpg" width="200" height="200" /></a>Mr. K.V. Madhan</strong> is a Chartered Accountant and the Managing Director of KVM Group of Companies. He has a wide experience of over 35 years in Taxation, Audit and Management Consultancy.\r\n\r\nHe has served as DGM – Taxation at Hyundai motor Company and the Executive Director of Ernst and Young. He is currently serving as a nominated member of the EOU and SEZ Council. He is involved in the drafting of Semi-Conductor Policy and SEZ Legislation.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clearall"></div>\r\n<a href="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Muralidhar.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-311 alignleft" alt="Muralidhar" src="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Muralidhar.jpg" width="200" height="200" /></a>Our academy is headed by <strong>Prof R. Muralidhar B.Sc, B.E (Mechanical), P.G.D.M IIM(Ahmedabad). </strong>He is a Non-Executive Director on the Board of IFB Industries, Kolkata and a Director in Pictoris Consulting Pvt. Ltd., a recruitment firm in Bangaluru. He is a strategist with expertise in keeping key focus on top and bottom line by optimum utilization of resources. He also has 37 years experience in achieving profit and business growth objectives with start-ups and turnarounds. He has held many managerial positions in his distinguished industrial career culminating as President, IFB Industries Ltd., Goa and an Independent Director in the same company.\r\n\r\nHe has had three year tenure as a full-time professor with Xavier Institute of Management, Bangaluru. His forte is operations management, strategic management and economics. His proudest moment was when he singled- handedly prepared XIME for NBA accreditation. As a result of his work, XIME was accorded accreditation for 5 years. He was also continuously chosen as the Best Teacher for 2 consecutive years.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h1>Director - Education</h1>\r\n<div><strong><a href="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Ramki-Murugan.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-273 alignleft" alt="Ramki Murugan" src="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Ramki-Murugan.jpg" width="200" height="200" /></a>Dr. M. Ramki Murugan ,</strong> a prominent professional with around three decades of industry experience and is the Director of education of KVM Academy. He is a Doctorate in Marketing with special reference to the Pharmaceutical Industry. He has a wide experience of around 30 years in reputed companies which include USV(Mumbai), Lotus Drugs, Bajaj Allianz etc.,. He has also provided consultancy services in Sales &amp; Marketing, Training &amp; Development, Marketing of Pharma Products and Life Insurance etc...He has rich experience in teaching at XIME Bangalore, AJK Institute of Management Coimbatore, Sree Vee Business School, R L Institute of Management Madurai and The American College Madurai. He was also a visiting faculty at Thyagarajar School of Management, Madurai.</div>\r\n<div class="clearall"></div>\r\n<strong><a href="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Shreyas.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-262 alignleft" alt="Shreyas" src="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Shreyas.jpg" width="200" height="200" /></a>Mr. Shreyas K Madhan,</strong> Director, an Architect by profession Mr Shreyas holds the position of Senior Manager at KVM Advisory Services Private Limited. He is also heading “Celestial Architects” , a team of Architects based out of Coimbatore who are actively into building residences, office spaces, factory sites and much more. Mr Shreyas is also a M.Sc. Creativity Management from UK and has an initiative “Light Bulb” with a friend which creates concepts and ideas for start-ups and help in building a brand name through "direct injection marketing"; Brand Building; Corporate films; Personality Development and so on. He also heads the Liaison/permit clearances department which aids companies to obtain building permit clearance at all levels. He has played a major part in the overall management of new strategies and initiatives taken up by KVM Group. He was earlier involved in designing and creating detailed architectural drawings for projects like schools, residences, hotels, hospitals and coordination with site. He is also experienced in the promotional and brand building activities for a famous township at Chennai.', 'Management Team', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '128-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-02-13 10:36:21', '2014-02-13 10:36:21', '', 128, 'http://kvmacademy.com/128-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(333, 1, '2014-02-13 10:36:18', '2014-02-13 10:36:18', '<h1><strong>Our Management Team</strong></h1>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n<strong> <a href="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Madhan.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-263 alignleft" alt="Madhan" src="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Madhan.jpg" width="200" height="200" /></a>Mr. K.V. Madhan</strong> is a Chartered Accountant and the Managing Director of KVM Group of Companies. He has a wide experience of over 35 years in Taxation, Audit and Management Consultancy.\r\n\r\nHe has served as DGM – Taxation at Hyundai motor Company and the Executive Director of Ernst and Young. He is currently serving as a nominated member of the EOU and SEZ Council. He is involved in the drafting of Semi-Conductor Policy and SEZ Legislation.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clearall"></div>\r\n<a href="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Muralidhar.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-311 alignleft" style="size-full wp-image-263 alignleft" alt="Muralidhar" src="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Muralidhar.jpg" width="200" height="200" /></a>Our academy is headed by <strong>Prof R. Muralidhar B.Sc, B.E (Mechanical), P.G.D.M IIM(Ahmedabad). </strong>He is a Non-Executive Director on the Board of IFB Industries, Kolkata and a Director in Pictoris Consulting Pvt. Ltd., a recruitment firm in Bangaluru. He is a strategist with expertise in keeping key focus on top and bottom line by optimum utilization of resources. He also has 37 years experience in achieving profit and business growth objectives with start-ups and turnarounds. He has held many managerial positions in his distinguished industrial career culminating as President, IFB Industries Ltd., Goa and an Independent Director in the same company.\r\n\r\nHe has had three year tenure as a full-time professor with Xavier Institute of Management, Bangaluru. His forte is operations management, strategic management and economics. His proudest moment was when he singled- handedly prepared XIME for NBA accreditation. As a result of his work, XIME was accorded accreditation for 5 years. He was also continuously chosen as the Best Teacher for 2 consecutive years.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h1>Director - Education</h1>\r\n<div><strong><a href="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Ramki-Murugan.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-273 alignleft" alt="Ramki Murugan" src="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Ramki-Murugan.jpg" width="200" height="200" /></a>Dr. M. Ramki Murugan ,</strong> a prominent professional with around three decades of industry experience and is the Director of education of KVM Academy. He is a Doctorate in Marketing with special reference to the Pharmaceutical Industry. He has a wide experience of around 30 years in reputed companies which include USV(Mumbai), Lotus Drugs, Bajaj Allianz etc.,. He has also provided consultancy services in Sales &amp; Marketing, Training &amp; Development, Marketing of Pharma Products and Life Insurance etc...He has rich experience in teaching at XIME Bangalore, AJK Institute of Management Coimbatore, Sree Vee Business School, R L Institute of Management Madurai and The American College Madurai. He was also a visiting faculty at Thyagarajar School of Management, Madurai.</div>\r\n<div class="clearall"></div>\r\n<strong><a href="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Shreyas.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-262 alignleft" alt="Shreyas" src="http://localhost/wp/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Shreyas.jpg" width="200" height="200" /></a>Mr. Shreyas K Madhan,</strong> Director, an Architect by profession Mr Shreyas holds the position of Senior Manager at KVM Advisory Services Private Limited. He is also heading “Celestial Architects” , a team of Architects based out of Coimbatore who are actively into building residences, office spaces, factory sites and much more. Mr Shreyas is also a M.Sc. Creativity Management from UK and has an initiative “Light Bulb” with a friend which creates concepts and ideas for start-ups and help in building a brand name through "direct injection marketing"; Brand Building; Corporate films; Personality Development and so on. He also heads the Liaison/permit clearances department which aids companies to obtain building permit clearance at all levels. He has played a major part in the overall management of new strategies and initiatives taken up by KVM Group. He was earlier involved in designing and creating detailed architectural drawings for projects like schools, residences, hotels, hospitals and coordination with site. He is also experienced in the promotional and brand building activities for a famous township at Chennai.', 'Management Team', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '128-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-02-13 10:36:18', '2014-02-13 10:36:18', '', 128, 'http://kvmacademy.com/128-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
